cff-version: 1.2.0
message: "If you use NoLimits.jl in your research, please cite it as below."
title: "NoLimits.jl"
abstract: >-
  A Julia framework for nonlinear mixed-effects modeling of longitudinal data,
  unifying mechanistic ODEs, hidden Markov models, neural-network and soft-tree
  components, and flexible random-effect distributions under frequentist,
  Bayesian, and variational estimation through a single fitting interface.
type: software
